<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>The Sociology minor complements any major and gives students a valuable skill set. Students learn to think critically, analyze complex situations, develop written and verbal communication skills, and understand the world around them in a new way. The minor gives students the flexibility to choose courses that fit their personal and career interests.</p>
